use R chunk -> if ((j < 4) || (j == 4))
{
  if ((j < 3) || (j == 3))
  {
    if ((j < 1) || (j == 1))
    {
      if ((j < 0) || (j == 0))
      {
        R0 = R0 + chunk;
      }
      else
      {
        R2 = R2 + chunk;
      }
    }
    else
    {
      R0 = R0 + chunk;
    }
  }
  else
  {
    R2 = R2 + chunk;
  }
}
else
{
  R1 = R1 + chunk;
}
use R rep -> R1 = R1 + rep;
resetPlaceHolder_1(); -> {
  // reset R2
  if (S1 < R1)
  {
    S1 = R1;
  }
  else
  {
    ;
  }
  R1 = 0;
  C1 = C1 + 1;
  // reset R0
}
resetPlaceHolder_2(); -> {
  // reset R2
  // reset R1
  if ((j < 4) || (j == 4))
  {
    if ((j < 2) || (j == 2))
    {
      if ((j < 1) || (j == 1))
      {
        if (S0 < R0)
        {
          S0 = R0;
        }
        else
        {
          ;
        }
        R0 = 0;
        C0 = C0 + 1;
      }
      else
      {
        // reset R0
      }
    }
    else
    {
      if (S0 < R0)
      {
        S0 = R0;
      }
      else
      {
        ;
      }
      R0 = 0;
      C0 = C0 + 1;
    }
  }
  else
  {
    // reset R0
  }
}

abstract class TemplateEngineSimplifiedVariant  {
  void execute(int text)
  {

    int BOOLEAN_SEPARATOR = 10;
    int C0 = -1;
    int C1 = -1;
    int C2 = -1;
    int D0 = 0;
    int D0p = 0;
    int D1 = 0;
    int D1p = 0;
    int D2 = 0;
    int D2p = 0;
    int temporaryText = 0;
    int lastIndexOfText = 0;
    lessPreciseBound(((((0 + (D0 + (D0p * (C0 - 1)))) + (D1 + (D1p * (C1 - 1)))) + (D2 + (D2p * (C2 - 1)))) < ((((8 * text) + (text * 10)) + (text * 30)) + 8)) || ((((0 + (D0 + (D0p * (C0 - 1)))) + (D1 + (D1p * (C1 - 1)))) + (D2 + (D2p * (C2 - 1)))) == ((((8 * text) + (text * 10)) + (text * 30)) + 8)));
    mostPreciseBound(((((0 + (D0 + (D0p * (C0 - 1)))) + (D1 + (D1p * (C1 - 1)))) + (D2 + (D2p * (C2 - 1)))) < ((text + (text * 10)) + (text * 30))) || ((((0 + (D0 + (D0p * (C0 - 1)))) + (D1 + (D1p * (C1 - 1)))) + (D2 + (D2p * (C2 - 1)))) == ((text + (text * 10)) + (text * 30))));
    if ((text < 1) || (text == 1))
    {
      return;
    }
    else
    {
      ;
    }
    int chunk = 0;
    int i = 0;
    while (i < text)
    {
      {
        temporaryText = ndInt2(lastIndexOfText, text);
        chunk = temporaryText - lastIndexOfText;
        lastIndexOfText = temporaryText;
      }
      D0 = D0 + chunk;
      D1 = D1 + 10;
      D2 = D2 + 30;
      i = i + 1;
      D2p = D2;
      D2 = 0;
      C2 = C2 + 1;
      D1p = D1;
      D1 = 0;
      C1 = C1 + 1;
      D0p = D0;
      D0 = 0;
      C0 = C0 + 1;
    }
  }

  public abstract int ndInt2(int lower, int upper);

  public abstract void lessPreciseBound(boolean assertion);

     (<= C0 0)))
(assert (let ((a!1 (< (+ 0 D0 (* D0p (- C0 1))) (+ (* types sep) types 1)))
      (a!2 (= (+ 0 D0 (* D0p (- C0 1))) (+ (* types sep) types 1))))
  (not (or a!1 a!2))))

(check-sat)
(get-model)

  public abstract void lessPreciseBound(boolean assertion);
}

  void execute(int sorted)
  {

    int BOOLEAN_SEPARATOR = 10;
    int C0 = -1;
    int C1 = -1;
    int D0 = 0;
    int D0p = 0;
    int D1 = 0;
    int D1p = 0;
    int temporarySorted = 0;
    int lastIndexOfSorted = 0;
    lessPreciseBound((((0 + (D0 + (D0p * (C0 - 1)))) + (D1 + (D1p * (C1 - 1)))) < ((8 * sorted) + 8)) || (((0 + (D0 + (D0p * (C0 - 1)))) + (D1 + (D1p * (C1 - 1)))) == ((8 * sorted) + 8)));
    mostPreciseBound((((0 + (D0 + (D0p * (C0 - 1)))) + (D1 + (D1p * (C1 - 1)))) < (sorted + (2 * sorted))) || (((0 + (D0 + (D0p * (C0 - 1)))) + (D1 + (D1p * (C1 - 1)))) == (sorted + (2 * sorted))));
    if ((sorted < 1) || (sorted == 1))
    {
      return;
    }
    else
    {
      ;
    }
    int entry = 0;
    int i = 0;
    while (i < sorted)
    {
      {
        temporarySorted = ndInt2(lastIndexOfSorted, sorted);
        entry = temporarySorted - lastIndexOfSorted;
        lastIndexOfSorted = temporarySorted;
      }
      int j = 0;
      while (j < entry)
      {
        D0 = D0 + 2;
        j = j + 1;
        D0p = D0;
        D0 = 0;
        C0 = C0 + 1;
      }
      D1 = D1 + 1;
      i = i + 1;
      D1p = D1;
      D1 = 0;
      C1 = C1 + 1;
    }
  }
  // Declare these methods such that these generated code can be parsed
  // Keep in sync with brbo2
  public abstract int ndInt();
  public abstract int ndInt2(int lower, int upper);
  public abstract boolean ndBool();
  public abstract void assume(boolean expression);
  public abstract void mostPreciseBound(boolean assertion);
  public abstract void lessPreciseBound(boolean assertion);
}

    int choice = 0;

        choice = temporaryChoices - lastIndexOfChoices;
        lastIndexOfChoices = temporaryChoices;

  void execute(int str)

    int BOOLEAN_SEPARATOR = 10;

    lessPreciseBound((R < ((8 * str) + 8)) || (R == ((8 * str) + 8)));

    while (i < str)
    {
      if (!((i < choice)) && !((i == choice)))
      {
        if (match)

          match = false;
          lastMatch = true;

abstract class SubstringsBetween  {
  void execute(int str)
  {

    int BOOLEAN_SEPARATOR = 10;
    int R = 0;
    lessPreciseBound((R < ((8 * str) + 8)) || (R == ((8 * str) + 8)));
    mostPreciseBound((R < str) || (R == str));
    if ((str < 0) || (str == 0))
    {
      return;
    }
    else
    {
      ;
    }
    int list = 0;
    int pos = 0;
    int open = 1;
    int close = ndInt2(0, str - 1);
    while (pos < (str - close))
    {
      int start = ndInt2(pos, str);
      if (start == str)
      {
        break;
      }
      else
      {
        ;
      }
      start = start + open;
      int end = ndInt2(start, str);
      if (end == str)
      {
        break;
      }
      else
      {
        ;
      }
      list = list + (end - start);
      R = R + (end - start);
      pos = end + close;
    }
  }
